Sentencas: Thermal cycling and thermal ageing tests were performed on Crofer22APU/glass-ceramic/Anode-Supported-Electrolyte (ASE) joined samples in air at the SOFC operating temperature of 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Thermal cycling and ageing of a glass-ceramic sealant for planar SOFCs

Sentencas: The Crofer22APU had been polished and preoxidised at 900 degrees C for 2 h. The diffusion behaviour at the two interfaces was examined and revealed slight diffusion of chromium and manganese from Crofer22APU into the glass-ceramic.
Titulo: Thermal cycling and ageing of a glass-ceramic sealant for planar SOFCs

Sentencas: No interactions, failure or crack formation were observed at the Crofer22APU/glass-ceramic interface and between the glass-ceramic and YSZ.
Titulo: Thermal cycling and ageing of a glass-ceramic sealant for planar SOFCs
